OL,3,C'Not forgotten': Fresh hope for long
OL,4,CCovid cure, five years on from pandemic
OL,6,FIt's been five years since Covid was
OL,7,Fdeclared a worldwide pandemic, and
OL,8,Flarge numbers of those who survived it
OL,9,Fare still feeling the effects - but
OL,10,Fthere is new hope for a treatment, as
OL,11,FITV News Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,12,FBarry reports
OL,14,FOn 11 March 2020, Becky Steed from
OL,15,FNottingham was working as GP in the
OL,16,FNHS.
OL,18,FThat was the day the World Health
OL,19,FOrganisation declared COVID-19 a
OL,20,Fglobal pandemic.
