OL,3,C'Not forgotten': Fresh hope for long
OL,4,CCovid cure, five years on from pandemic
OL,6,FBecky continued her work on the
OL,7,Ffrontline, until she contracted the
OL,8,Fvirus. Her life has never been the
OL,9,Fsame since.
OL,11,F"I've been to some really dark places
OL,12,Fthese last few years, really dark
OL,13,Fplaces," Becky told ITV News.
OL,15,FShe is one of around two million
OL,16,Fpeople in the UK living with long
OL,17,FCovid.
OL,19,FNo longer able to work as a GP, Becky
OL,20,Fcan only perform her new job, training
OL,21,FNHS staff, if she is lying down.
