OL,3,C'Not forgotten': Fresh hope for long
OL,4,CCovid cure, five years on from pandemic
OL,6,F"At my worst I was using a wheelchair
OL,7,Fto get out of the house," she said.
OL,8,F"If I stand up I get palpitations. If
OL,9,FI lie down, my brain works, If I stand
OL,10,Fup, my brain stops working."
OL,12,FShe feels long Covid has re-defined
OL,13,Fher: "It is like a bereavement. It's a
OL,14,Floss of the person that I was, it's a
OL,15,Floss of the life I had."
OL,17,FBut most painful, has been the impact
OL,18,Fon her family.
