OL,3,C'Not forgotten': Fresh hope for long
OL,4,CCovid cure, five years on from pandemic
OL,6,F"I think as a mum it hurts more,
OL,7,Fbecause there are things I can't do
OL,8,Fwith my little boy," she told me. "It
OL,9,Fleaves you with a feeling that you've
OL,10,Ffailed as a mum."
OL,12,FFive since the start of the pandemic,
OL,13,Flong Covid sufferers like Becky are
OL,14,Fstill living with the disabling
OL,15,Feffects of the condition.
OL,17,FSymptoms can include extreme fatigue,
OL,18,Fdifficulty concentrating and muscle
OL,19,Faches.
