OL,3,C'Not forgotten': Fresh hope for long
OL,4,CCovid cure, five years on from pandemic
OL,6,FBecky is one of 70 people taking part
OL,7,Fin a study at the University of Derby.
OL,9,FITV News was given exclusive access to
OL,10,Fto film the research, the first of
OL,11,Fit's kind in the UK.
OL,13,FScientists are investigating whether
OL,14,Fanti-viral drugs, often used to treat
OL,15,Fpeople hospitalised with Covid, could
OL,16,Fprovide an effective treatment for
OL,17,Flong Covid.
