OL,3,C'Not forgotten': Fresh hope for long
OL,4,CCovid cure, five years on from pandemic
OL,6,FIt's been six months since the first
OL,7,Fpatients received the medication and
OL,8,Fsome are already reporting an
OL,9,Falleviation of their symptoms.
OL,11,F"It is vital research for the people
OL,12,Fwho are living with long Covid now -
OL,13,Fbut also the people who will go on to
OL,14,Fdevelop long Covid in the future"
OL,15,FProfessor Mark Faghy, who is leading
OL,16,Fthe study, told ITV News.
OL,18,FHe hopes the research will eventually
OL,19,Flead to a treatment for long covid
OL,20,Fbecoming available on the NHS.
