OL,3,C'Not forgotten': Fresh hope for long
OL,4,CCovid cure, five years on from pandemic
OL,6,F"We have a responsibility to make sure
OL,7,Fwe can find ways to help people."
OL,9,FBecky had her first dose two months
OL,10,Fago and feels the drugs are already
OL,11,Fhelping.
OL,13,F"It's given me hope - and that's
OL,14,Fsomething which has been really
OL,15,Flacking these last few years.
OL,17,F"It helps you feel that you've not
OL,18,Fbeen forgotten."
